---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Computer Service FAQ Dallas Fort Worth | Common Questions | GadgetFix"
  description="Answers to common questions about computer services in Dallas Fort Worth. Service times, security, service areas, and more. Mobile service available."
  keywords="computer service questions, virus removal time, password reset service, mobile computer service dallas"
>
  <main class="faq-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions - Computer Service Dallas Fort Worth</h1>
      
      <div class="faq-intro">
        <p>Get answers to common questions about our mobile computer services in the Dallas-Fort Worth area. 
        Can't find your answer? Call us at <a href="tel:4694308607">(469) 430-8607</a>.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <!-- Service FAQs -->
        <section class="faq-section">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-icon">
              <svg role="img" aria-label="Service and repair icon" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Service & Repair Questions</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How long does virus removal take?</h3>
            <p>Most <a href="/virus-removal-service" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">virus removals</a> take 30-60 minutes. <a href="/password-reset-service" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Password resets</a> typically take 15-30 minutes, 
            <a href="/computer-optimization" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">computer optimization</a> takes 30-45 minutes, and full system cleanups take 45-60 minutes. We complete services 
            on-site while you wait, whether at your home, office, or preferred location in DFW.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you come to my location?</h3>
            <p>Yes! We're a 100% mobile service covering all of Dallas-Fort Worth. We come to your home, 
            office, coffee shop, or any safe public location. Our service area includes <a href="/locations/dallas-county/dallas" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Dallas</a>, <a href="/locations/tarrant-county/fort-worth" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Fort Worth</a>, <a href="/locations/dallas-county/plano" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Plano</a>, 
            <a href="/locations/collin-county/frisco" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Frisco</a>, <a href="/locations/dallas-county/irving" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Irving</a>, <a href="/locations/tarrant-county/arlington" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Arlington</a>, and surrounding cities within a 30-mile radius.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What areas do you serve?</h3>
            <p>We serve the entire Dallas-Fort Worth metroplex including: <a href="/locations/dallas-county" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Dallas County</a> (Dallas, Richardson, Garland), 
            <a href="/locations/tarrant-county" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Tarrant County</a> (Fort Worth, Arlington, Grand Prairie), <a href="/locations/collin-county" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Collin County</a> (Plano, Frisco, McKinney, Allen), 
            and <a href="/locations/denton-county" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Denton County</a> (Denton, Lewisville, Flower Mound). Typical arrival time is 30 minutes.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you fix all computer problems?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we fix all software-related computer issues including viruses, malware, slow performance, 
            password problems, software installation, and network issues. We specialize in Windows and Mac computers. 
            We serve <a href="/emergency-computer-service" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">emergency computer service</a> cases throughout Dallas-Fort Worth.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you provide estimates?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we provide professional diagnostics and transparent estimates for all computer issues. If your computer won't start or has unknown problems, 
            we'll diagnose it and provide a clear service quote. You only pay if you approve the service. Call us for an instant quote over the phone.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Warranty FAQs -->
        <section class="faq-section">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-icon">
              <svg role="img" aria-label="Warranty and quality icon" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
                <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Warranty & Quality Questions</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What guarantee do you offer?</h3>
            <p>All services come with our satisfaction guarantee. If you experience any issues 
            with the service we provided, we'll return to fix it at no additional charge. We guarantee complete 
            virus removal and full password recovery on all supported systems.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you use quality software tools?</h3>
            <p>We use professional, licensed software tools from industry leaders like Microsoft, Norton, and Malwarebytes. 
            Our tools are always up-to-date with the latest virus definitions and security patches. We never use pirated 
            or questionable software on your computer.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Will I lose my data during service?</h3>
            <p>No, virus removal and most common services don't affect your data. Your files, photos, documents, 
            and settings remain intact. For severe infections or system issues, we always attempt data preservation first. 
            We recommend backing up your computer before any service as a precaution.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Are your technicians certified?</h3>
            <p>Yes, our technicians are experienced professionals with extensive training in computer software services. 
            They stay updated on the latest virus removal techniques and security tools and use professional-grade software 
            to ensure quality service.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Device-Specific FAQs -->
        <section class="faq-section">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-icon">
              <svg role="img" aria-label="Device specific icon" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Computer-Specific Questions</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can you reset Windows passwords?</h3>
            <p>Yes, our technicians are experts at <a href="/password-reset-service" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Windows password reset</a>. 
            We can reset local accounts, Microsoft accounts, and administrator passwords without data loss. We use professional 
            tools to regain access while preserving all your files and programs.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you service Mac computers?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we specialize in <a href="/computer-optimization" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Mac computer services</a> including macOS password reset, virus removal, and optimization. 
            Our technicians are experienced with all Mac models including MacBook Pro, MacBook Air, iMac, and Mac Mini. 
            Most services take about 30-45 minutes.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Which Windows versions do you support?</h3>
            <p>We support all <a href="/password-reset-service" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">Windows versions</a> including Windows 11, Windows 10, Windows 8.1, and Windows 7. 
            We can remove viruses, reset passwords, optimize performance, and install software on all these versions. 
            We also support Windows Server editions for business clients.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you fix laptop computers?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we service all laptop brands including Dell, HP, Lenovo, ASUS, and Acer. 
            Common services include <a href="/virus-removal-service" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">virus removal</a>, password reset, and performance optimization. We provide 
            on-site service for both personal and business laptops.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Booking FAQs -->
        <section class="faq-section">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-icon">
              <svg role="img" aria-label="Booking and scheduling icon" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/>
                <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
                <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Booking & Scheduling Questions</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Are you open on weekends?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we're open 7 days a week including weekends. Our hours are Monday through Sunday, 8:00 AM to 6:00 PM. 
            Weekend appointments fill quickly, so we recommend calling early to schedule your preferred time.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you offer emergency computer service?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we offer <a href="/emergency-computer-service" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">emergency same-day computer service</a> throughout Dallas-Fort Worth. For urgent issues, 
            we typically arrive within 30 minutes to 1 hour. Emergency service is available for virus removal, password reset, and critical issues. 
            Call <a href="tel:4694308607">(469) 430-8607</a> for immediate assistance.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I schedule computer service?</h3>
            <p>Simply call us at <a href="tel:4694308607">(469) 430-8607</a> to schedule. We'll ask about your computer type, 
            the issue, and your preferred location and time. We'll provide a quote over the phone and can often 
            come the same day. You can also visit our <a href="/contact" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline;">contact page</a> for more information.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What should I do before the technician arrives?</h3>
            <p>Back up your important files if possible, note any error messages you're seeing, and choose a comfortable 
            location for the service. Make sure your computer is plugged in or charged. Have your login credentials 
            ready if you remember them - if not, we can help reset them.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Process FAQs -->
        <section class="faq-section">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-icon">
              <svg role="img" aria-label="Repair process icon" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="m12 19 7-7 3 3-7 7-3-3z"/>
                <path d="m18 13 3-3-3-3-3 3 3 3z"/>
                <path d="m2 6 3-3 3 3-3 3-3-3z"/>
                <path d="M9 10h1l6-6-1-1-6 6v1z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Repair Process Questions</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What happens during a mobile repair?</h3>
            <p>Our technician arrives at your location with all necessary tools and parts. They'll diagnose your device, 
            confirm the issue and quote, complete the repair while you wait, test all functions, and clean your device. 
            The entire process typically takes 30 minutes for most repairs.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Is mobile repair as good as shop repair?</h3>
            <p>Yes! We bring professional-grade tools and parts to your location. Our mobile setup is complete with 
            everything needed for quality repairs. The only difference is convenience - you don't have to drive anywhere 
            or wait in a shop.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What if the repair takes longer than expected?</h3>
            <p>If we discover additional issues during repair, we'll explain the situation and provide options. 
            You're never obligated to proceed with additional repairs. Most repairs are completed within the estimated 
            time frame.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
            <p>We accept cash, all major credit cards, debit cards, and mobile payment apps. Payment is due when 
            the repair is completed. We provide receipts for your records and warranty documentation.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
      
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h2>Still Have Questions?</h2>
        <p>We're here to help! Call us for immediate answers or to schedule your repair.</p>
        <a href="tel:4694308607" class="cta-button">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="margin-right: 8px;">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
          </svg>
          Call Now: (469) 430-8607
        </a>
        <p class="service-note">Mobile Repair Service • 7 Days a Week • 8AM-6PM</p>
        <p class="additional-info">Learn more about <a href="/services" style="color: #2563EB;">our services</a> or <a href="/about" style="color: #2563EB;">about our company</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
.faq-page {
